{"tid":2048313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你同意梁振英在1989年6月5日對中共血腥屠殺人民的譴責嗎？","createTime":"2020-06-02T16:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T20:20:30.000Z","uid":351574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af3e3551e2ba4dd625a27c60564b3e0cf0916419","tid":2048313,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=d41b4b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1</a><br />\n1989年六四事件發生，梁振英於6月5日在報章刊登署名聲明：「強烈譴責中共當權者血腥屠殺中國人民」，又向「開天窗」表示不滿的《文匯報》致崇高敬意。他接受電台訪問時沉痛說：「六四事件是中國政府的一個重大錯誤，嚴重性很大，我感到悲哀同無助<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120524/16363930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120524%2F16363930&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=1d2acb93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120524%2F16363930&h=483d3310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120524/16363930</a><br />\n1989年6月5日<br />\n梁振英在報章刊登署名廣告，譴責中共血腥屠殺人民"},{"pid":"611d5263b0f70d976331839d5ef5942c330f74df","tid":2048313,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"689:屠殺利多於弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ece158a19ff3679f4b357da7e6003040e22301","tid":2048313,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply